----- Original Message -----
From: <cbuckbee@...>
To: <EQ_Necromancer@onelist.com>
Sent: Saturday, September 04, 1999 12:03 AM
Subject: [EQ_Necromancer] List Activity


> From: cbuckbee@...
>
> I have noticed that there are currently 163 members on this list. For
this amount of people we should be seeing a lot more activity. Lets try to
keep this list going by helping each other out. Even if you don't have a
question, just let us know how things are going in game or let us know how
your gaming has been going so far. I think one way to do this is everyone
should send in a mail with their characters info (Name, Level, Race, Server,
etc.). This would help the rest of us to see who all is on our individual
servers and hopefully make friends to adventure with. I guess I will start
this off since it's my idea.
>
> Branil
> Dark Elf
> 14th Level
> Quellious
>
> Currently camped in the Lake Rathe zone at the gnoll camp. If you see me
in game give me a tell.
>
> Happy gaming everyone.
